#: ../../quickstart.rst:2 de43b6699dec4383a9d081298cf9847c
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "Quick Start"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:4 410ccb91b6ed441faf89300dd2b201ba
msgid ""
"This page gets you from zero to a working VoxCPM setup as fast as possible. "
"Follow it top to bottom and you will have generated audio through three "
"different paths: the Python API, the CLI, and the web demo."
msgstr "本页会尽可能快速地带你从零完成可运行的 VoxCPM 安装。按顺序往下操作后，你就可以通过三种方式生成语音：Python API、CLI 和网页演示。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:7 a365ccc5311343e28686467d61c324d3
msgid "Install"
msgstr "Install"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:13 b2b652a2939549019076cd5f57f832ce
msgid ""
"That's it. For other installation methods (pip, source checkout, etc.), see "
":doc:`./installation`."
msgstr "到这里就完成了。若你想了解其他安装方式（如 pip、从源码安装等），请参阅 :doc:`./installation`。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:16 ef872a5eedf9436da2f68a5971987492
msgid "Step 1: Python API"
msgstr "Step 1: Python API"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:18 c6a7e9a042744220b53643d9dfbb2dbf
msgid "Start with the current recommended release, ``VoxCPM 2``:"
msgstr "从当前推荐版本 ``VoxCPM 2`` 开始："

#: ../../quickstart.rst:38 f69b636166eb4c10b921f770d3d93447
msgid ""
"The first run downloads model weights automatically. If you have trouble "
"accessing Hugging Face, see the mirror setup in :doc:`./installation`."
msgstr "首次运行会自动下载模型权重。如果你访问 Hugging Face 有困难，请查看 :doc:`./installation` 中的镜像配置。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:40 d1335457f5fb4e4fb28cae7e2287ad2f
msgid ""
"This example does not enable the optional denoiser — it is only needed when "
"you want to enhance prompt or reference audio for voice cloning. See "
":doc:`./usage_guide` for details."
msgstr ""
"这个示例没有启用可选降噪器。只有当你想在声音克隆时增强 prompt 或 reference 音频时才需要它。详情见 "
":doc:`./usage_guide`。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:42 6a15b6d511014834aafa76aaa038fa41
msgid "If this script runs and produces ``demo.wav``, your installation is working."
msgstr "如果这段脚本可以正常运行并生成 ``demo.wav``，说明你的安装已可正常工作。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:46 9f7f5aaea70147efb750fde7921de527
msgid ""
"For new projects, start with :doc:`./models/voxcpm2`, which is the current "
"version. Earlier releases remain available from "
":doc:`./models/version_history` when you need an older checkpoint."
msgstr ""
"对于新项目，建议从当前版本 :doc:`./models/voxcpm2` 开始。如果你需要较旧的 checkpoint，也可以在 "
":doc:`./models/version_history` 中找到早期版本。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:49 c785b3db3c3e4ce195421c7b9e6ee84d
msgid "Step 2: CLI"
msgstr "Step 2: CLI"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:51 7e793387ba754caca126ae7728684021
msgid ""
"VoxCPM also provides a command-line interface. The CLI defaults to "
"``openbmb/VoxCPM2``, so you can use the recommended subcommands directly "
"unless you want to override the checkpoint with ``--hf-model-id``:"
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 也提供命令行接口。CLI 默认使用 ``openbmb/VoxCPM2``，因此除非你想通过 ``--hf-model-id`` 覆盖 "
"checkpoint，否则可以直接使用推荐子命令："

#: ../../quickstart.rst:71 7aa051ca868840deb77f03859cc17d44
msgid "Step 3: Web Demo"
msgstr "Step 3: Web Demo"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:73 95834788c0de45b89ea50428d676df68
msgid ""
"The web demo requires a source checkout. If you installed via ``pip install "
"voxcpm`` in the step above, you still need to clone the repository:"
msgstr "网页演示需要克隆源码仓库。如果你在上一步通过 ``pip install voxcpm`` 完成安装，仍然需要克隆仓库："

#: ../../quickstart.rst:82 c595bedd75e34806b1ab3957eb9678c5
msgid ""
"The web demo also downloads an additional ASR model (SenseVoice-Small) on "
"first use for prompt audio transcription."
msgstr "Web Demo 在首次使用时还会额外下载一个 ASR 模型（SenseVoice-Small），用于 prompt 音频转写。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:85 73244143b01945b0b46045731b4af374
msgid "What's Next?"
msgstr "What's Next?"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:87 1dd62bde074f4469987238e961f8be9f
msgid ""
"Continue with :doc:`./usage_guide` for prompt strategy, voice cloning tips, "
"and quality tuning."
msgstr "继续阅读 :doc:`./usage_guide`，了解 prompt 策略、声音克隆技巧和质量调优。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:88 52b81d3ce66d4689a99ce4abe500e2d0
msgid ""
"Check the pages under ``Models`` in the sidebar for version-specific "
"features and migration notes."
msgstr "查看侧边栏 ``Models`` 下的页面，了解各版本特性与迁移说明。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:89 383d3cef05f04ea9bafb31be8326e4c1
msgid ""
"Fine-tune the model with :doc:`./finetuning/finetune` to adapt it to your "
"use case."
msgstr "通过 :doc:`./finetuning/finetune` 微调模型，使其适配你的实际场景。"

#: ../../quickstart.rst:90 d4855e47032e421fbe44bf0cb137a567
msgid ""
"Deploy the model with :doc:`./deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm` for high-"
"throughput serving."
msgstr "通过 :doc:`./deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm` 部署模型，以实现高吞吐服务。"

